<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70A9901003" svcinfotypenbr = "03" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Description of Anti-Pinching Function
</title>
<ptxt>
The anti-pinching function reverses and then stops the auto-slide-closing sun roof when a load exceeding the preset value is applied to the sun roof glass (1) due to pinching of something, etc.
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9901003001">
<title>
Reverse Operation Stroke of Anti-Pinching Function
</title>
<ptxt>
When a load exceeding the preset value is applied to the auto-slide-closing sun roof glass, it reverses by approx. 125 mm (4.92 in.).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
The sun roof glass stops its motion if it opens fully before moving 125 mm (4.92 in.).
</ptxt>
