<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9901003002">
<title>
Sun Roof Fail-Safe Function
</title>
<ptxt>
Sun roof control module in sun roof motor stops auto sliding and auto tilting.
</ptxt>
<topic id = "AENAP70A9901003003">
<title>
Fail-safe condition
</title>
<ptxt>
Magnetic sensor pulse count exceeds memorized MAX position data.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
There is no signal from one magnetic sensor while there is signal from another magnetic sensor.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70A9901003004">
<title>
Fail-safe cancel condition
</title>
<ptxt>
After initialization of sun roof motor.
</ptxt>
</topic>
